{"tid":1158661,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[超過850人加入] Discord電台 之 想講一講「逃犯條例」","createTime":"2019-05-17T06:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T04:49:41.000Z","uid":43718,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce666495e71909785396f7ce1b718fe904ba644c","tid":1158661,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前言</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n最近發現Discord原來有個bot可以一路播歌 一路傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱小弟喺外國身邊又無咩做 所以想睇下有無巴絲打同我一樣無咩嘢做 又想搵嘢聽下 咪入黎傾下計吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有心事感情學業工作煩惱都可以係度分享 睇下咁其他巴打有無咩意見畀到你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得閒仲可以點下歌開心share大家音樂既興趣 無聊想廢up下都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要係要禁入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">-----------------------------------------------------</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">節目時間表</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">星期三</span></span> [[[2300 - 0000 吹水]]] [[[0000 - 0115 木人巷之鬼]]]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">星期五</span> </span> [[[2300 - 0000 吹水]]] [[[0000 - 0115 感情台]]]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">星期日</span></span> [[[2300 - 0000 吹水]]] [[[0000 - 0130 駐台歌手]]]</div><br />\n<br />\n詳情歡迎加入頻道後查詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 不時都會有突發開台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">-----------------------------------------------------</div><br />\n<br />\n而家已經有超過「<span style=\"color: gold;\">850<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span></span>」個巴絲打入咗頻道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣就入嚟聽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以試下Call-In<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqFTfqpc&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=7ddc41ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「入咗台嘅巴絲打記住要開notification 方便追蹤本台最新消息」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"8ae182f3990ec1ff13c8ac8904adf24814783238","tid":1158661,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01717afa941be1e92a30382f565d10f189bf83df","tid":1158661,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792aecf9fdbced26366c855bd3d40d3465423c6b","tid":1158661,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2520474747e406412a0cf98e8e1e9d3013ea3745","tid":1158661,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e21cab38f79e399358f13e275ba69cbefc40cf2","tid":1158661,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"